## Important Safety Notice

This software is a PROTOTYPE for demonstration and educational purposes only. 
It is NOT intended for use with live railway systems or operational technology.

**CRITICAL SAFETY WARNINGS:**
- Do NOT connect this software to live railway signaling systems
- Do NOT use in production environments without proper safety certifications
- Do NOT deploy without regulatory approval and safety validation
- This software uses simulated data only and has not been validated for safety-critical applications

The authors and contributors disclaim any responsibility for any damage, injury, 
or loss that may result from the use of this software in any context other than 
controlled demonstration environments.

For production use, this software would require:
- Formal safety verification and validation
- Regulatory approval from relevant railway authorities
- Integration with certified safety systems
- Comprehensive testing and validation procedures
- Professional safety engineering review

Use at your own risk and only in appropriate demonstration contexts.